Create a file if not exists :   /etc/network/interfaces

    ADD THE FOLLOWING LINES:



auto eth0
iface eth0 inet static
address 192.168.1.15            #------> Your Ip Address (To be assigned as static)
netmask 255.255.255.0           #------> Netmask
gateway 192.168.1.254           #-------> Gateway
broadcast 192.168.0.255 
dns-nameservers 192.168.1.3     #-----> Dns server





After that: sudo service network-manager restart